<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c4">[٧١٠]</span> أَبُو المُخَارِقِ <span class="c2">(٢)</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>رَوى عنهُ الأَعْمشُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>يُعدُّ في الكُوفِيِّينَ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>عنِ النبيِّ -صلى اللَّه عليه وسلم-.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
