<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c4">[٧١٢]</span> أَبُو مَطرٍ البَصْريُّ <span class="c2">(٤)</span>.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>سمِعَ عَلِيًّا.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>رَوى عنهُ المُخْتارُ بنُ نافعٍ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c4">[٧١٣]</span> أَبُو مَطَرٍ <span class="c2">(٥)</span>.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
